snippet.title: Mark Wahlberg Talks to Animals - SNL
snippet.description:
Mark Wahlberg (Andy Samberg) goes for a walk around a farm, talking to all the animals about his movies and asking them to "say hi to your mother for me." [Season 34, 2008]
